title: Haste.the.Day
description:
Haste the Day was an American Christian metalcore band signed with Solid State Records that was formed in Carmel, Indiana in 2001. Their name is derived from a lyric in the hymn "It Is Well With My Soul." The band released an EP titled That They May Know You, in 2002, followed by five studio albums: Burning Bridges (2004), When Everything Falls (2005), Pressure the Hinges (2007), Dreamer (2008), and Attack of the Wolf King (2010). The group disbanded in March 2011.
